\pard\plain \s120\fi-360\li360\widctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls1\pnrnot0\pndec }\ls1\adjustright \fs20\cgrid 
A dealer chooses a secret polynomial {\i f(x)}  with degree {\i t-1} , such that its constant term is the secret to be shared {\i s} .\par
\pard\plain \s120\fi-360\li360\widctlpar\jclisttab\tx360{\*\pn \pnlvlbody\ilvl0\ls1\pnrnot0\pndec }\ls1\adjustright \fs20\cgrid 
The dealer sends the tuple *(x{\sub i} , f(x{\sub i} ))* as the share to {\i i} -th user, where *x{\sub i} *'s are all non-zero and distinct for {\i i = 1, \'85 , n} .\par}
\par
\par}
{\bkmkstart AAAAAAAAAF}
{\bkmkend AAAAAAAAAF}
